# Environment Variables example for Vantage Robotics Simulation

# You can use EITHER an OpenAI key OR an Anthropic key.
# The server-side proxy automatically detects the key type and routes to the appropriate model (GPT-4o-mini or Claude Sonnet).
#
# Do NOT prefix with VITE_ to prevent it from leaking to the browser.

# Option A: OpenAI API Key (used for both Voice Whisper Transcription and Agentic AI)
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Option B: Anthropic API Key (if you prefer using Claude for the Agentic AI)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here
